column29:
People don't really think or talk about their mental health, especially when it comes to men. From managing professional life to personal life to taking responsibility of aging parents to pressure of staring their own family men go through alot and don't get enough opportunities to speak or express themselves enough about it.
It's important we give men the chance to speak about their feeling and emotions without judging them for their masculinity.
